creator: Punam Wagh
descriptionHtml:
Introducing PAWAN WAGH ACADEMY'S Application.
1. PWA is the platform made for all in which all your topic wise video lectures by your favorite lecturers of our PWA team have been organized in a structured manner by their classes and their respected subjects.
2. Get Daily updates of our latest videos on our app making it easy to navigate to youtube and study.
3. Get Inspired by your favorite Pawan Wagh Sir thoughts daily in the "Mann ki Baat" section.
4. Introducing the powerful feature of the "Live Quiz". Live Quiz platform will enable you to test your knowledge and skills among thousands of students competing live on the platform with all the control in the respected faculty. Not only this Top 5 performers who have answered right and topped the charts will be displayed on the faculty's screen with the calculations in the millionth of a second and at the end of the Live Quiz top 10 Scorers will be displayed on the each and everyone's screen along with the summary of your performance.
5. Introducing PWAidea! In this platform, students will be served with notes alongside QR Codes for every topic which will navigate you to the exact timestamp of that video, making it simple to understand to everyone without wasting time on searching, scrolling, and all messy kinds of stuff.
6. Stay tuned for more amazing features...

~ Follow Us ~
